\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left|\psi\right\rangle \otimes\left|0\right\rangle _{m}\otimes\left|\varphi\right\rangle _{c}.
\end{equation}

\end_inset

The ion can now be controlled to its ground state using coherent quantum
 feedback.
 First focus light on the system ion and drive a spin-selected 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

 pulse.
 This pulse takes 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\uparrow\right\rangle \otimes\left|0\right\rangle _{m}$
\end_inset

 to 
\begin_inset Formula $-i\left|\downarrow\right\rangle \otimes\left|1\right\rangle _{m}$
\end_inset

 and vice versa while leaving 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\downarrow\right\rangle \otimes\left|0\right\rangle $
\end_inset

